@@$TJvCheckBox
<TITLE TJvCheckBox overview>
<GROUP JVCL.Miscel>
  TJvCheckBox is a check box descendant that has an auto save feature, and hot track capability. In
  addition a control can be associated with the check box. Checking the check box will enable the
  control, unchecking the check box will disable the control.
