@@TJvCheckBox.Associated
Summary
  Reference to an associated control.
Description
  Associated holds a reference to an associated control. The associated control's \Enabled property
  will automatically follow the value of the Checked property.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCheckBox.AutoSave
Summary
  Specifys the location to save the check box state in.
Description
  AutoSave defines the location where to store the state of the Checked property in. When the
  control is read in from the form stream, the state is read from this location.
