@@TJvCheckBox.HotTrack
Summary
  Enables or disables hot tracking.
Description
  HotTrack enables or disables the hot tracking feature of the control.

  When set to True hot tracking is enabled and the Caption will be rendered in the font specified by
  HotTrackFont when the mouse is over the control.

  When set to False hot tracking is disabled.
See Also
  HotTrackFont
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCheckBox.HotTrackFont
Summary
  Font used when the mouse is over the control and hot tracking is enabled.
Description
  HotTrackFont indicates the font used to render the Caption in when the mouse is over the control
  and hot tracking is enabled (HotTrack is set to True).
See Also
  HotTrack
